Type: Package
Package: HatchedPolygons
Title: Create a hatched area for SpatialPolygons
Version: 0.3.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    c(
        person(given = "Sébastien",
               family = "Rochette",
               role = c("aut", "cre"),
               email = "sebastienrochettefr@gmail.com"),
        person(given = "Gregory R.",
               family = "Warnes",
               role = c("ctb"),
               email = "greg@warnes.net")
  )
Maintainer: Sébastien Rochette <sebastienrochettefr@gmail.com>
Description: This package allows to create a area filled by
    SpatialLines to allow for hatched areas in SpatialPolygons.  This may
    be particularly useful when SpatialPolygons show holes but also for
    drawing hatched areas in leaflet Polygons.
License: GPL-3
